sentence: What are the prerequisites for EECS 203 and 280 ?
sentence-with-vars: What are the prerequisites for department0 number0 and number1 ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE AS COURSEalias1 , COURSE_PREREQUISITE AS COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0 WHERE ( COURSEalias1.NUMBER = 203 OR COURSEalias1.NUMBER = 280 ) AND COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.PRE_COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias1.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" ;
